electivity, should generally be avoided in patients with bronchospastic diseases.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/292492/', '', 'Felodipine, Acetylsalicylic acid, Amlodipine, Nifedipine, Amlodipine, Valsartan, Irbesartan, Losartan, Olmesartan, Azilsartan medoxomil, Telmisartan, More', 'Mometasone furoate, Umeclidinium, Aclidinium, Mometasone, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Ipratropium, Tiotropium, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
